An alumni panel discusses how to prepare for technical interviews, and human resources teams jot notes on tablets as students introduce themselves. Recruiters distribute tote bags filled with branded notebooks, pens, water bottles, and phone chargers. A data science company showcases a live dashboard of fair attendance. After the fair, friends decompress on the quad, comparing which companies responded warmly and discussing various swag items they received.

Workshops on networking etiquette begin in the adjoining classroom, where career counselors remind attendees to maintain eye contact. A welcome announcement outlines the fair schedule over the PA system. As the fair progresses, chimes signal the final hour, prompting small groups to analyze which recruiters seemed most enthusiastic. Near the exit, a post-event survey link flashes on the monitors.

Students exit with tote bags and a stack of business cards, while small groups analyze which recruiters seemed most enthusiastic.
